<tr id="L311"><td><a href="#L311">311</a></td><td>UHURA [OC]:  It is with great regret that we cannot honour that request. Intergalactic treaty clearly specifies that no being can be extradited without due process. In view of the circumstances, we have no doubt that after a hearing at Starbase, Commissioner Bele will be permitted to retain his prisoner and be provided transportation</td></tr>

